snippet.title: Nintendo Switch 「QV」 Meet the Characters #1: Quby
snippet.description:
Proudly presenting QV, an inter-dimensional action adventure game for Nintendo Switch!
Let's meet the protagonist, Quby, in the first character teaser!
She explores the old ruins to find a key to save the dimensions in crisis!
Stay tuned for Quby's adventurous tale! 

- Official Twitter Account : https://twitter.com/QV_NEWS
